      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 80,
      "message": "Actually I haven't found the common pattern as the images are often entered in different way and not all of the images in the charts are used in the deployment. I thing there should be a way how to do that without the helm, but haven't found out how to do that yet. So I decided to use the helm to get the relevant list of the images in three different patterns only.",
