      "file_path": "build/creating_data/docker-images-collector.sh",
      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 87,
      "message": "Helm is using yaml. \nPlease describe here what different conventions helm uses and how it unifies the end result. We sure can parse all the different conventions purely with yaml too. Then we see whihc one is simpler. It's really not simple if we need to use helm for this.",
